# ── Terraform state and provider cache ──────────────────────────────────────
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/terraform.tfstate.*.backup

# ── Cluster credentials (written by bootstrap stage) ────────────────────────
iac/clusters/*/credentials/

# ── Per-cluster secrets (SOPS-encrypted, but still sensitive — keep local) ──
iac/clusters/*/secrets/

# ── Editor and OS noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
